items.text: full, offcutter on middle stump, deceived completely. Tries to turn this towards square leg, but can't make contact
items.shortText: Mashrafe Mortaza to Moor, no run

items.text: another offcutter outside off, but this time it's been lifted over cover. Hit well enough to beat wide long off
items.shortText: Mashrafe Mortaza to Moor, FOUR runs

items.text: good length on off stump, goes deep into the creaes and punches through to long on
items.shortText: Shakib Al Hasan to Cremer, 1 run

items.text: good length on middle stump, tapped down the ground once again. The man at long on comes into action once again
items.shortText: Shakib Al Hasan to Moor, 1 run

items.text: full on off stump, hit back to Shakib
items.shortText: Shakib Al Hasan to Cremer, no run

items.text: full on middle, and it's swept away. Hit well past the square-leg umpire to deep backward point
items.shortText: Shakib Al Hasan to Cremer, 1 run

items.text: flatter on off stump, goes onto the back foot, and punched to mid on
items.shortText: Shakib Al Hasan to Moor, 1 run

items.text: tossed up on middle stump, and the punch off the back foot takes a leading edge. Falls just short of the diving short extra cover fielder.
items.shortText: Shakib Al Hasan to Cremer, 1 run

items.text: back of a length outside off, turns into the batsman, muscled off the back foot to wide long on.
items.shortText: Nasir Hossain to Cremer, 1 run

items.text: full outside off, driven back past the non-striker to long on. The ball seems to be following that position
items.shortText: Nasir Hossain to Moor, 1 run

items.text: full on off stump, Cremer walks across to the off side and tries to flick this to the leg side. Hits his pad, but the around-the-wicket angle doesn't help the lbw cause
items.shortText: Nasir Hossain to Cremer, no run

items.text: good length on middle, worked behind square off the back foot to fine leg
items.shortText: Nasir Hossain to Cremer, 1 run

items.text: big appeal! But turned down again. Attempts a sweep to this full ball but misses
items.shortText: Nasir Hossain to Moor, no run

items.text: tries the reverse sweep! This one doesn't come off either, takes his pad as he attempts the shot. Lobs up, but falls in front of his pads, just about far enough from the keeper
items.shortText: Nasir Hossain to Moor, no run

items.text: overpitched on middle stump, bunted down the ground to wide long on. Muscled away past the non-striker
items.shortText: Shakib Al Hasan to Cremer, 1 run

items.text: flighted full outside off, driven to cover
items.shortText: Shakib Al Hasan to Moor, no run

items.text: tossed up outside off, big wind up to slog this over cow corner. Stays low, and misses completely as the ball straightens after pitching. Barely misses off stump
items.shortText: Shakib Al Hasan to Moor, no run

items.text: full on off stump, zips through this time. Blocked back to Shakib
items.shortText: Shakib Al Hasan to Moor, no run

items.text: dispatched away! Short outside off, enough room for Moor to free his arms. Goes back and pulls along the ground to the cow-corner boundary
items.shortText: Shakib Al Hasan to Moor, FOUR runs

items.text: full outside off, another attempted cross-batted slog, but doesn't come off this time. Played to wide long on
items.shortText: Shakib Al Hasan to Moor, 1 run

items.text: full on off stump, stroked away wide of cover, hit well to deep extra cover. They want the second, and Cremer is halfway down when Moor sends him back. Moor's looking at the ball instead of Cremer. But the throw is at the wrong end. Survives
items.shortText: Mustafizur Rahman to Moor, 1 run

items.text: full on off stump, hit down the ground to long off once again
items.shortText: Mustafizur Rahman to Cremer, 1 run

items.text: good length pitching outside leg, extra bounce off the pitch as he nudges this with the shoulder of his bat to square leg. Hit softly enough
items.shortText: Mustafizur Rahman to Moor, 1 run

items.text: good length on leg stump, fended back to Fizz off the back foot
items.shortText: Mustafizur Rahman to Cremer, no run

items.text: good length on leg stump, carved off the back foot to cover. Loud and early call for the single
items.shortText: Mustafizur Rahman to Cremer, 1 run
